rows.label: campfev11_490_175_msg0003
rows.name: What happens if you get desert fever?

rows.label: campfev11_490_175_msg0005
rows.name:
Your lungs get infected, and you get
sick like you had a cold or something.

rows.label: campfev11_490_175_msg0006
rows.name:
Oh... Well, if that's all it is, maybe it's
not much to worry about...

rows.label: campfev11_490_175_msg0008
rows.name:
But if you're unlucky, it can spread to
your skin, joints, bones, liver and
kidneys. And if that happens...

rows.label: campfev11_490_175_msg0011
rows.name:
Let's not worry, Sata.
I know Prince Adel, and I know
he'll get the medicine made for sure.
